flow-state|deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm|graduated|This pattern moves from depth into ideas, then into response, with physical rhythm as deliberate range. The result is strongest when private work becomes clear without staying trapped in thought and talk.|You can develop work privately and then make it clearer through response.|You may leave movement or recovery until the mind has already done too much.|Use the sequence, then bring in pace, movement, or setting before continuing.|Think, open, explain, then change state.|active|flow-state::deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange_physical_rhythm::graduated
